movie.title: Collateral
movie.plot: Cab driver Max picks up a man who offers him $600 to drive him around. But the promise of easy money sours when Max realizes his fare is an assassin.
movie.awards: Nominated for 2 Oscars. Another 23 wins & 68 nominations.
